"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1148401","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2019-10-08","<p>My Department will be publishing the government response to the consultation ‘Future delivery of support to victims and their children in accommodation-based domestic abuse services’ shortly.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","Thornbury and Yate","Luke Hall",,"2019-10-08T14:28:32.093Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1148401/answer","Biography information for Luke Hall","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1148401/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1148401/answer",,,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2019-10-04","Housing: Domestic Abuse","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, with reference to his Department's consultation on Domestic abuse services: future delivery of support to victims and their children in accommodation-based domestic abuse services, which closed on 2 August 2019, when the response to that consultation will be published.","false","Biography information for Sarah Champion","Rotherham","Sarah Champion","294726"
